Ten times the rains had come and gone.

16
00:05:31,900 --> 00:05:36,440
我经常顺便去看看人兽过得怎样了
And I often stopped by to see how Mowgli the man cub was getting along.

17
00:05:36,610 --> 00:05:39,940
