哦，你还可以
Oh, there you are.

168
00:17:09,100 --> 00:17:12,970
脚后跟并拢，好不好？儿子
Let's keep those heels together, shall we, son?

169
00:17:13,140 --> 00:17:15,640
好，爸爸。长官
Okay, Pop. Sir.

170
00:17:15,770 --> 00:17:18,100
对，现在好多了。
Yes, now that's better.

171
00:17:18,230 --> 00:17:22,140
噢，新兵，恩？
Well, a new recruit, eh?

172
00:17:22,270 --> 00:17:24,270
我说，你鼻子怎么啦？
I say, what happened to your trunk?

173
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:26,270
嘿！别那样！
Hey! Stop that!

174
00:17:27,610 --> 00:17:30,900
人兽！ 噢，这是背叛 ！
A man cub! Oh, this is treason!

175
00:17:31,020 --> 00:17:34,280
蓄意破坏! 我不会让我的丛林里出现人兽！
Sabotage! I'll have no man cub in my jungle!

176
00:17:34,440 --> 00:17:39,490
我-这不是你的丛林！-别吵了！别吵了！我来解释一下，哈索
I-It's not your jungle! -Hold it! Hold it! I can explain, Hathi.

177
00:17:39,650 --> 00:17:42,150
哈索上校 如果可以的话，长官
Colonel Hathi, If you please, sir.

178
00:17:42,320 --> 00:17:45,490
哦，好，好 哈索上校
Oh, yes, yes. Colonel Hathi.

179
00:17:45,660 --> 00:17:49,950
恩，人兽是和我在一起的 我正带着他返回人类村庄
Uh, the man cub is with me. I'm taking him back to the man village.

180
00:17:50,120 --> 00:17:53,660
留下来？- 你有了巴吉拉的命令
To stay? - You have the word of Bagheera.

181
00:17:53,780 --> 00:17:59,160
好，记住 大象从不忘事的
Good. And remember, an elephant never forgets.

182
00:18:01,660 --> 00:18:04,370
我不知道现在部队要怎样
I don't know what the army's coming to these days.

183
00:18:04,460 --> 00:18:06,710
那些年轻的傲慢的家伙 他们以为他们是谁？
These young whippersnappers, who do they think they are?

184
00:18:09,250 --> 00:18:12,790
我们继续！ 向右看！
Let's get on with it! Right face!

185
00:18:12,960 --> 00:18:15,090
前进！
Forward march!

186
00:18:22,960 --> 00:18:26,340
亲爱的，你没忘记什么吧？
Dear, haven't you forgotten something?

187
00:18:26,510 --> 00:18:30,890
废话，威尼弗雷德老太婆 大象从不忘事的
Nonsense, Winifred old girl. An elephant never forgets.

188
00:18:31,050 --> 00:18:34,550
哦，你惟独忘记了我们的儿子
Well, you just forgot our son.

189
00:18:34,680 --> 00:18:36,970
恩，恩，儿子--儿子？
Uh, uh, son-- Son?

190
00:18:37,100 --> 00:18:39,970
儿子！噢，对，对呀，对呀！ 说得对
Son! Oh, yes, yeah, yeah! Quite right.

191
00:18:40,140 --> 00:18:42,010
向后转！齐步走！
To the rear! March!

192
00:18:46,520 --> 00:18:50,270
我长大后，我要当上校，就象我爸爸那――
When I grow up, I'm gonna be a Colonel, just like my--

193
00:18:50,390 --> 00:18:53,350
我说过一次，就要和说过一千次一样――-噢！
If I've told you once, I've told you a thousand times-- Oh!

194
00:18:53,480 --> 00:18:55,940
爸爸！小心！
Pop! Look out!

195
00:19:09,070 --> 00:19:12,110
哎，爸爸，你忘了说“立定”了
Gee, Pop, you forgot to say "halt."

196
00:19:14,360 --> 00:19:16,700
他说过大象从不忘事的
He said an elephant never forgets.

197
00:19:21,080 --> 00:19:23,280
这并不好笑
It's not funny.

198
00:19:23,410 --> 00:19:26,620
趁其他什么事情发生前 立即离开这
Now let's get out of here quick before anything else happens.

199
00:19:31,410 --> 00:19:34,620
巴吉拉！我们要去哪里？
Bagheera! Where are we goin'?

200
00:19:34,790 --> 00:19:38,290
你就要回到人类村庄
You're going back to the man village right now.

201
00:19:38,460 --> 00:19:42,130
我不想去 -噢，你非去不可
I'm not going  - Oh, yes, you are!

202
00:19:42,250 --> 00:19:44,340
我就待在这里！
I'm staying right here!

203
00:19:44,500 --> 00:19:47,960
就算我拖着你走，你也得走
You're going if I have to drag you every step of the way.

204
00:19:50,670 --> 00:19:53,340
让我走，你-- - 你放开我！
Let go, you- - You let go of me!

205
00:20:03,090 --> 00:20:06,010
哦，就这样定了
Oh, that does it.

206
00:20:06,140 --> 00:20:08,890
我受够了，人兽！
I've had it, man cub!

207
00:20:09,010 --> 00:20:14,140
从现在开始，你一个人好自为之！
From now on, you're on your own alone!

208
00:20:14,270 --> 00:20:16,730
别担心我
Don't worry about me.

209
00:20:46,700 --> 00:20:49,070
愚蠢的人兽
Foolish man cub.

210
00:21:18,300 --> 00:21:21,260
嘟-哔 嘟-哔 嘟-哔 嘟-哔
Doo-bee doo-bee doo-bee-dee-doo

211
00:21:21,420 --> 00:21:25,720
哦，嘟―吧―的―嘟 对，嘟―吧―的―嘟
Well, it'sa doo-bah-dee-doo Yes, it'sa doo-bah-dee-doo

212
00:21:25,880 --> 00:21:30,970
我说的是嘟―哔 嘟―哔，嘟―哔 嘟―哔，嘟―哔―嘟―哔
l mean a doo-bee doo-bee, doo-bee doo-bee, doo-bee-dee-doo

213
00:21:31,090 --> 00:21:32,890
和―
And with--

214
00:21:33,050 --> 00:21:35,970
好吧，现在
Well, now.

215
00:21:36,100 --> 00:21:37,970
看看这是什么呢？
What have we here?

216
00:21:42,770 --> 00:21:47,060
嘿，多有趣的小―
Hey, what a funny little bit of a--

217
00:21:47,230 --> 00:21:49,390
噢！ - 走开！
Oh! - Go away!

218
00:21:49,560 --> 00:21:53,520
哦，小男孩，这个林子里我啥都见过了
Oh, boy, I've seen everything in these woods.

219
00:21:53,690 --> 00:21:56,690
呼！我说什么来着？ 多么可爱的家伙
Hoo! What have I run on? What a pretty thing this is.

220
00:21:56,860 --> 00:22:00,110
别理我  - 好
Leave me alone  - Well, now.

221
00:22:00,270 --> 00:22:03,110
多么可爱的大话! 小家伙
That's pretty big talk, little britches.

222
00:22:03,280 --> 00:22:05,110
我够大了
I'm big enough.

223
00:22:07,990 --> 00:22:12,240
遗憾啊，嘿，小孩, 你需要帮助
Pitiful. Hey, kid, you need help.

224
00:22:12,400 --> 00:22:16,110
老布鲁来教你怎样像熊一样打架
And old Baloo's gonna learn you to fight like a bear.

225
00:22:16,240 --> 00:22:18,110
来吧，我来示范
Now come on, I'm gonna show you.

226
00:22:22,160 --> 00:22:24,120
对！
Yeah!

227
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:27,910
好吧，孩子，放松。完全放松然后开始晃动身体
All right, now, kid, loosen up. Get real loose and then start to weave.

228
00:22:28,080 --> 00:22:30,410
晃动一点点 现在开始移动! 就这样!
Weave a little. Now move! That's it!

229
00:22:30,540 --> 00:22:33,370
现在，给我一个熊的咆哮 吓唬我
Now give me a big bear growl. Scare me.

230
00:22:37,290 --> 00:22:39,330
哦，男孩
Oh, boy.

231
00:22:39,500 --> 00:22:42,420
我说的是像头大熊
I'm talkin' about like a big bear.

232
00:22:48,380 --> 00:22:50,960
他遇到麻烦了！ 咳，我―我不应该留下他一个人的
He's in trouble! Why, I-I shouldn't have left him alone.

233
00:22:57,930 --> 00:23:00,930
一个大的咆哮，用尽全身的力气 - 感觉怎么样？
A big one. Right from your toes  - How's that?

234
00:23:06,970 --> 00:23:11,890
对，你学会了，孩子 - 噢，不！是布鲁
Yeah, you're gettin' it, kid  - Oh, no! It's Baloo.

235
00:23:12,060 --> 00:23:15,270
那个无能的愚蠢的丛林流浪汉
That shiftless, stupid jungle bum.

236
00:23:15,390 --> 00:23:17,980
左右晃动，寻找空当.
Weave about now and look for an opening.

237
00:23:18,140 --> 00:23:19,980
继续前进，继续-
Keep movin'. Keep--

238
00:23:20,140 --> 00:23:23,150
做得好，你学会了，孩子 再来，就这样
Yeah, you're gettin' it, kid. Come on, that's it.

239
00:23:25,190 --> 00:23:27,560
他棒极了
He's a dandy.

240
00:23:30,650 --> 00:23:33,820
真是个好老师, 老铁爪
Fine teacher you are, old iron paws.

241
00:23:33,980 --> 00:23:37,690
哦，谢谢，巴吉拉 - 恩，告诉我，告诉我，恩...
Oh, thanks, Bagheera  - Eh, tell me, tell me, uh...

242
00:23:37,860 --> 00:23:42,900
你把你的学生撞晕之后, uh, 你还指望他记住你教的吗？恩？
after you knock your pupil senseless, uh, how do you expect him to remember the lesson? Hmm?

243
00:23:43,070 --> 00:23:48,910
这个, 我-- 我, uh-- 这个, 我没想要把他摔那么重
Well, I-- I, uh-- Well, I didn't mean to lay it on him so hard.

244
00:23:49,070 --> 00:23:51,990
我没伤着, 挺好的
I'm not hurt. I'm all right.

245
00:23:52,120 --> 00:23:54,240
我比有些人想象的要强壮
I'm a lot tougher than some people think.

246
00:23:54,370 --> 00:23:56,410
你最好相信这点
You better believe it.

247
00:23:56,540 --> 00:24:01,000
我们再来一次，我要你一直绕圈，要不然我又要撞到你的背了
Now let's go once more.Now I want you to keep circlin' or I'm gonna knock your roof in again.

248
00:24:01,160 --> 00:24:03,000
你要不停地动
You better keep movin'.

249
00:24:03,160 --> 00:24:06,000
嘿! 正好打在我下巴上！
Hey! Right on the button.

250
00:24:15,170 --> 00:24:17,500
不，不，不, 你弄得我很痒
No, no-no, no-no. Now you're ticklin'.

251
00:24:19,840 --> 00:24:23,510
不！不。我们别在丛林里这样
No! No. N-N-Now, now we don't do that here in the jungle.

252
00:24:23,630 --> 00:24:28,430
不，弄得我很痒 我-我受不了这么痒
No, you're ticklin'. I-I can't stand that ticklin'.

253
00:24:28,550 --> 00:24:33,010
救命，巴吉拉！- 噢，孩子，那是他想要的，使劲挠
Help, Bagheera! - Oh, boy, that's all he needs. More confidence.

254
00:24:33,180 --> 00:24:36,470
投降，布鲁？ - 跟你说，我投降
Give up, Baloo? - I give up, I told ya.

255
00:24:36,600 --> 00:24:39,010
嚯！嘿！
Ooh! I give-- Hey!

256
00:24:40,970 --> 00:24:45,020
你知道了？你是对的，孩子。 他们叫你什么？
You know somethin'? You're all right, kid. What do they call you?

257
00:24:45,140 --> 00:24:49,190
毛戈力。他马上就要回人类村庄了
Mowgli. And he's going back to the man village right now.

258
00:24:49,350 --> 00:24:53,150
人类的村子? 他们会毁了他，他们会把他变回一个"人"
Man village? They'll ruin him. They'll make a man out of him.

259
00:24:53,270 --> 00:24:56,020
哦，布鲁，我要和你待在这
Oh, Baloo, I wanna stay here with you.

260
00:24:56,150 --> 00:24:58,150
那当然
Certainly you do.

261
00:24:58,270 --> 00:25:02,690
噢？你觉得他怎么活下去？
Oh? And just how do you think he will survive?

262
00:25:02,860 --> 00:25:07,240
你觉得他-―― 你指什么，你觉得他――
"How do you think he will--" What do you mean, "How do you think he--"

263
00:25:07,360 --> 00:25:10,530
他和我在一起，不是吗？ 我会教给他我知道的一切
He's with me, ain't he? And I'll learn him all I know.

264
00:25:10,700 --> 00:25:13,900
哦，最好不要太久
Well, that shouldn't take too long.

265
00:25:14,780 --> 00:25:19,070
看，就像这样 小不点
Look, now it's like this, little britches.

266
00:25:19,240 --> 00:25:22,080
你要做的一切是――
All you've gotta do is--

267
00:25:22,200 --> 00:25:27,410
寻找最起码的生活必需品  最起码的生活必需品
Look forthe bare necessities  The simple bare necessities

268
00:25:27,580 --> 00:25:31,370
忘记你的恐惧和矛盾
Forget about your worries And your strife

269
00:25:31,540 --> 00:25:36,500
我的意思是，最基本的需要，是天性中的东西
I mean the bare necessities are Mother Nature's recipes

270
00:25:36,670 --> 00:25:40,750
生命中本能的需要
That bring the bare necessities of life

271
00:25:40,920 --> 00:25:45,420
不管我逛到哪儿,晃到哪儿
Wherever I wander Wherever I roam

272
00:25:45,590 --> 00:25:50,130
最喜欢的仍是我的家
I couldn't be fonder of my big home

273
00:25:50,300 --> 00:25:55,300
蜜蜂在花丛中嗡嗡，为我酿蜜
The bee sare buzzin' in the tree to make some honey just for me

274
00:25:55,470 --> 00:25:57,880
你往石头和植物下面看
When you look under the rocks and plants

275
00:25:58,050 --> 00:26:00,010
看一眼那些可爱的蚂蚁
And take a glance at the fancy ants

276
00:26:00,180 --> 00:26:02,010
或许可以尝几个
Then maybe try a few

277
00:26:02,140 --> 00:26:04,550
你吃蚂蚁吗？
You eat ants?

278
00:26:04,680 --> 00:26:09,060
你最好相信，你会喜欢上它们在你舌头上爬来爬去的感觉
You better believe it. And you're gonna love the way they tickle.

279
00:26:09,220 --> 00:26:11,060
毛戈力，小心！
Mowgli, look out!

280
00:26:11,180 --> 00:26:15,720
生活必需品会有的 - 什么时候会有？
The bare necessities of life will come to you - But when?

281
00:26:15,850 --> 00:26:18,100
会有的
They'll come to you

282
00:26:18,230 --> 00:26:23,520
寻找最起码的生活必需品 那最起码的必需品
Look for the bare necessities The simple bare necessities

283
00:26:23,650 --> 00:26:27,400
忘记你的恐惧和矛盾
Forget about your worries And your strife

284
00:26:27,560 --> 00:26:30,360
我是说最基本的需要
I mean the bare necessities

285
00:26:30,480 --> 00:26:32,730
这就是一头熊为什么可以逍遥自在
That's why a bear can rest at ease

286
00:26:32,860 --> 00:26:36,820
只需要那最起码的生活必需品
With just the bare necessities Of life

287
00:26:36,940 --> 00:26:39,150
当你摘仙人掌
Now when you pick a paw paw

288
00:26:39,280 --> 00:26:41,530
或者刺梨 - 哎哟！
Or a prickly pear - Ow!

289
00:26:41,650 --> 00:26:46,110
你的手掌被刺到了 下次要小心
And you prick a raw paw Well, next time, beware

290
00:26:46,280 --> 00:26:48,410
不要直接用手掌
Don't pick the prickly pear By the paw

291
00:26:48,570 --> 00:26:51,240
摘梨时 试着用你的指甲
When you pick a pear Try to use the claw

292
00:26:51,370 --> 00:26:56,620
不过摘比较大的果子的时候,不要用你的指甲
But you don't need to use the claw When you pick a pear of the big paw paw

293
00:26:56,790 --> 00:27:00,550
我说清楚了吗? - 真神。谢谢。布鲁
Have I given you a clue? - Golly. Thanks, Baloo.

294
00:27:00,710 --> 00:27:02,550
木瓜
Pawpaw.

295
00:27:02,710 --> 00:27:04,920
什么玩意儿
Of all the silly gibberish.

296
00:27:05,090 --> 00:27:07,170
好了，布吉, 把它打下来
Come on, Baghee, get with the beat.

297
00:27:07,300 --> 00:27:11,800
生活必需品会有的 - 我会有的!！
The bare necessities of life will come to you - They'll come to me!

298
00:27:11,930 --> 00:27:14,430
你会有的
They'll come to you

299
00:27:14,550 --> 00:27:18,470
抓上面那儿 肩膀左边，毛戈力？
How 'bout scratchin' that ol' left shoulder while you're up there, Mowgli?

300
00:27:18,640 --> 00:27:22,720
头低下一点 在那，就在那。对了。
Now just a hair lower. There. Right there. That's it.

301
00:27:22,850 --> 00:27:26,140
哦！太舒服了
Oh! This is beautiful.

302
00:27:26,270 --> 00:27:31,390
不错。孩子，我们要上树 痛痛快快的搔搔
That's good. Kid, we've got to get to a tree. This calls for some big scratchin'.

303
00:27:31,520 --> 00:27:33,390
你太有趣了。布鲁
You're lots of fun, Baloo.

304
00:27:35,220 --> 00:27:37,470
就在这上面。耶！
Right on it. Yeah!

305
00:27:39,930 --> 00:27:42,180
真舒服
That's delicious.

306
00:27:44,270 --> 00:27:47,270
有那么一点--
Just a little bit--

307
00:27:47,390 --> 00:27:49,270
耶！
Yeah!

308
00:28:01,820 --> 00:28:03,650
耶
Yeah.

309
00:28:10,990 --> 00:28:14,490
哦，--朋友, 这才是真正的活着
Oh, man, this is really livin'.

310
00:28:15,990 --> 00:28:19,950
只要试着放松
So just try and relax.

311
00:28:20,120 --> 00:28:22,490
耶。冷静下来
Yeah. Cool it.

312
00:28:22,660 --> 00:28:26,290
我家后院的瀑布
Fall apart in my backyard.

313
00:28:26,410 --> 00:28:29,120
让我来告诉你,小家伙
'Cause let me tell you somethin', little britches.

314
00:28:29,250 --> 00:28:31,790
如果你象蜜蜂一样
If you act like that bee acts...

315
00:28:31,910 --> 00:28:36,160
恩，你干得太辛苦了
uh-uh, you're workin' too hard.

316
00:28:36,290 --> 00:28:40,130
不花费时间四处寻找...
And don't spend your time lookin' around...

317
00:28:40,250 --> 00:28:45,290
那些你想要却得不到的东西
for something you want that can't be found.

318
00:28:45,420 --> 00:28:49,840
当你发现没有它，你可以照样过，就会不再想它
When you find out you can live without it and go along not thinkin' about it

319
00:28:50,010 --> 00:28:53,010
我来告诉你个真理
I'll tell you somethin' true

320
00:28:53,170 --> 00:28:58,010
你将拥有生活必需品
The bare necessities of life will come to you

321
00:28:58,180 --> 00:29:01,840
我投降, 我希望他会一直好运气
I give up. Well, I hope his luck holds out.

322
00:29:02,010 --> 00:29:04,600
毛戈力，你来唱一下,怎么样?
Mowgli, how 'bout you sing?

323
00:29:04,720 --> 00:29:09,970
寻找最基本的需要 最基本的需要
Look for the bare necessities The simple bare necessities

324
00:29:10,140 --> 00:29:13,970
忘记你的担忧和矛盾 - 耶，朋友
Forget about your worries and your strife  - Yeah, man.

