就很危险,这取决于你
he's in danger, so it's up to you.

493
00:43:00,150 --> 00:43:03,740
为什么是我？ - 因--因--因为他不听我的
Why me? - Be-Be-Because he won't listen to me.

494
00:43:05,070 --> 00:43:07,740
我爱那孩子
I love that kid.

495
00:43:07,870 --> 00:43:09,790
我爱他就像我自己的孩子
I love him like he was my own cub.

496
00:43:09,950 --> 00:43:13,420
那么想想什么对毛戈力最好，而不是对你
Then think of what's best for Mowgli and not yourself.

497
00:43:13,580 --> 00:43:17,300
能否-那么, 我可以等到天亮再....?
Uh, well, can't-- Well, can't I wait until morning?

498
00:43:17,420 --> 00:43:19,300
已经天亮了
It's morning now.

499
00:43:22,050 --> 00:43:24,300
来吧，布鲁
Go on, Baloo.

500
00:43:29,650 --> 00:43:31,480
恩--
Uh--

501
00:43:44,960 --> 00:43:47,120
哦，孩子
Oh, boy.

502
00:43:49,130 --> 00:43:52,090
毛戈力，毛戈力
Mowgli. Mowgli.

503
00:43:52,420 --> 00:43:54,680
该起床了
Uh, it's time to get up.

504
00:43:56,510 --> 00:43:58,720
哦。你好，布鲁
Oh. Hi, Baloo.

505
00:43:58,890 --> 00:44:02,940
把那些瞌睡虫从你眼睛里赶走
Hi. Hey, rub that old sleep out of your eyes.

506
00:44:04,020 --> 00:44:07,190
你和我，我们还有很长一段路要走
You and me, uh, we got a long walk ahead of us.

507
00:44:07,320 --> 00:44:10,570
大熊，我们在一起会有很多快乐
Swell. Gee, we'll have lots of fun together.

508
00:44:11,950 --> 00:44:16,450
那当然 对了，恩--
Sure. Yeah. Yeah. Uh--

509
00:44:16,620 --> 00:44:19,420
好吧, 上路吧, 孩子
All right, let's hit the trail, kid.

510
00:44:19,540 --> 00:44:22,790
回见 恩，巴吉拉.
See ya around, uh, Bagheera.

511
00:44:22,960 --> 00:44:24,840
再见，巴吉拉
Well, goodbye, Bagheera.

512
00:44:25,010 --> 00:44:28,010
布鲁和我，我们有很多事情要做
Me and Baloo, we've got things to do.

513
00:44:28,180 --> 00:44:32,470
再见, 孩子，祝你好运
Goodbye, man cub. And good luck.

514
00:44:32,640 --> 00:44:35,770
来吧，布鲁 我们要做的是――
Come on, Baloo. All we gotta do is--

515
00:44:35,940 --> 00:44:38,610
寻找生活必需品
Look for the bare necessities

516
00:44:38,690 --> 00:44:40,940
一些生活必需品
Some good old bare necessities

517
00:44:41,110 --> 00:44:45,070
忘记你的担忧和矛盾
Forget about your worries And your strife

518
00:44:45,240 --> 00:44:47,950
我是说生活必需品
l mean the bare necessities

519
00:44:48,080 --> 00:44:50,250
那就是为什么熊可以逍遥自在
That's why a bear can rest at ease

520
00:44:50,410 --> 00:44:54,120
仅仅拥有生活必需品
With just the bare necessities of life

521
00:44:54,250 --> 00:44:56,960
耶，我会生活在这丛林里
Yeah I'll live here in the jungle

522
00:44:57,090 --> 00:44:59,800
一辈子, 耶
All my life Yeah, man

523
00:44:59,970 --> 00:45:02,550
我喜欢做一只熊
I like bein' a bear.

524
00:45:04,010 --> 00:45:08,140
我们在往哪儿走，布鲁？ -哦，恩，去--，恩--
Where we goin', Baloo? - Well, uh, it's, uh--

525
00:45:08,310 --> 00:45:10,980
恩，哦，这次去一个新地方 恩――
Um, well, it's sort of new and, uh--

526
00:45:11,110 --> 00:45:13,860
哦，我不在意，只要和你在一起.
Oh, I don't care,as long as I'm with you.

527
00:45:15,320 --> 00:45:18,030
毛戈力，恩，听着, 伙计, 恩--
Mowgli, uh, look, buddy, uh...

528
00:45:18,160 --> 00:45:20,200
有些事情我得告诉你.
there's somethin' I gotta tell ya.

529
00:45:20,330 --> 00:45:22,660
告诉我什么，布鲁？
Tell me what, Baloo?

530
00:45:22,830 --> 00:45:25,710
唉
Gee whiz.

531
00:45:25,870 --> 00:45:29,090
老布鲁该怎么说? 这, uh--
Now how did old Baghee put it? It's, uh--

532
00:45:29,320 --> 00:45:31,880
恩，恩，毛戈力？
Uh, uh, Mowgli?

533
00:45:32,010 --> 00:45:36,090
哈！你不会娶一头豹子, 是不是?
Ha! You wouldn't marry a panther, would you?

534
00:45:36,260 --> 00:45:40,100
我不知道你在说什么
Gee, I don't even know what you're talkin' about.

535
00:45:40,220 --> 00:45:43,560
毛戈力，你没有认识到你是一个人类吗?
Mowgli, don't you realize that you're a human?

536
00:45:43,730 --> 00:45:46,770
我不再是了，布鲁。我是一头熊，就像你一样。
I'm not any more, Baloo. I'm a bear like you.

537
00:45:47,050 --> 00:45:48,650
小伙计, 来,听我说.
Little buddy, look, listen to me.

538
00:45:48,820 --> 00:45:51,820
来吧，来吧，布鲁  - 毛戈力，停下，停下
Come on. Come on, Baloo - Now, Mowgli, stop it now.

539
00:45:51,990 --> 00:45:54,450
别乱跑. 我-我想跟你好好谈谈
Now hold still. I-I want to tell you something.

540
00:45:54,620 --> 00:45:56,490
现在听我说
Now listen to me.

541
00:45:56,660 --> 00:45:59,160
怎么啦。老熊爸爸？ 听着 -毛戈力---
What's the matter, old Papa Bear? - Look, Mowgli...

542
00:45:59,330 --> 00:46:02,080
我要告诉你，我一上午都在想告诉你.
I been tyin' to tell ya. I been tyin' all morning to tell ya.

543
00:46:02,210 --> 00:46:05,550
我要把你送回人类的村子
I've got to take you back to the man village.

544
00:46:05,920 --> 00:46:07,670
人类村庄！- 孩子，听我说--
The man village! - Now look, kid...

545
00:46:08,010 --> 00:46:10,590
我可以解释--- 可是, 你说我们是伙伴.
I can explain, and-- - But, but you said we were partners.

546
00:46:10,760 --> 00:46:14,270
相信我，孩子，我-我-我-- -你就像，就像老巴吉拉！
Now believe me, kid, I-I-I-- - You're just like, like old Bagheera!

547
00:46:14,430 --> 00:46:17,770
就一会儿，太过分了
Now just a minute. That's goin' too far.

548
00:46:20,230 --> 00:46:22,230
嘿，毛戈力， 你要去哪里？
Hey, Mowgli, where you goin'?

549
00:46:23,740 --> 00:46:25,700
等一等！站住！
Wait a minute! Stop!

550
00:46:26,950 --> 00:46:29,080
等等！
Wait!

551
00:46:29,200 --> 00:46:31,910
等等！听听老布鲁的
Wait! Listen to old Baloo.

552
00:46:32,080 --> 00:46:34,670
毛戈力，毛戈力！
Mowgli. Mowgli!

553
00:46:36,000 --> 00:46:38,000
毛戈力！
Mowgli!

554
00:46:40,800 --> 00:46:45,470
- 毛戈力。毛戈力！- 发生什么了?
- Mowgli. Mowgli! - Now what's happened?

555
00:46:45,640 --> 00:46:48,220
你, 你, 你大概不会相信我, 巴吉拉---
Well, you, you, you're not gonna believe me, Bagheera...

556
00:46:48,390 --> 00:46:52,730
可是, 我照你说的那样说了, 然后他就跑了.
but look, now I used the same words you did, and he ran out on me.

557
00:46:52,770 --> 00:46:54,690
好啦，别光站在那儿
Well, don't just stand there.

558
00:46:54,820 --> 00:46:58,200
我们分头找吧。我们-- 我们一定要找到他
Let's separate.We-- We've got to find him.

559
00:46:58,370 --> 00:47:00,490
噢，如果这小家伙出了什么事---
Oh, if anything happens to that little guy...

560
00:47:00,620 --> 00:47:03,330
我永远不能原谅我自己
I'll never forgive myself.

561
00:47:03,500 --> 00:47:06,460
我一定要找到他， 毛戈力！
I gotta find him. Mowgli!

562
00:47:08,210 --> 00:47:10,040
毛戈力！
Mowgli.

563
00:47:57,150 --> 00:47:59,440
嘿，二，三，四
Hup, two, three, four

564
00:47:59,570 --> 00:48:01,650
嘿，二，三，四
Hup, two, three, four

565
00:48:01,820 --> 00:48:03,780
不松劲 二，三
Keep it up Two, three

566
00:48:03,950 --> 00:48:06,320
真不走运
What beastly luck.

567
00:48:06,490 --> 00:48:09,160
那个可笑的哈索上校真讨厌
Confound that ridiculous Colonel Hathi.

568
00:48:09,290 --> 00:48:11,870
部队, 安静
Company, sound off.

569
00:48:12,000 --> 00:48:14,170
我们到处行军
Oh, we march from here to there

570
00:48:14,330 --> 00:48:16,840
不论到哪儿
And it doesn't matter where

571
00:48:17,000 --> 00:48:19,510
你可以听到我们穿过灌木丛
You can hear us push through the deepest bush

572
00:48:19,670 --> 00:48:21,720
嘿，二，三，四
Hup, two, three, four

573
00:48:21,840 --> 00:48:24,260
伴随军乐曲
With a military air

574
00:48:24,530 --> 00:48:27,100
伴随军乐曲
With a military air

575
00:48:29,690 --> 00:48:32,190
丛林巡逻
The jungle patrol.

576
00:48:34,440 --> 00:48:36,820
我们是无敌雄师
We're a cracker jack brigade

577
00:48:37,070 --> 00:48:39,240
在阅兵场上
On a pachyderm parade

578
00:48:39,410 --> 00:48:42,240
但我们宁愿在泥沼里穿行
But we'd rather stroll to a waterhole

579
00:48:42,370 --> 00:48:44,330
嘿，二，三，四
Hup, two, three, four

580
00:48:44,450 --> 00:48:46,960
在树荫下休息
For a furlough in the shade

581
00:48:48,080 --> 00:48:50,920
停下! 等--等一会
Stop! W-Wait a minute.

582
00:48:51,050 --> 00:48:53,130
立定！
Halt!

583
00:48:54,880 --> 00:48:58,550
是谁说的立定？这里由我发令！
Who said halt? I give the commands around here.

584
00:48:58,720 --> 00:49:03,890
大声说，你是谁？ - 哦，是我，上校
Now speak up. Who was it? - Oh, it was me, Colonel.

585
00:49:04,270 --> 00:49:06,230
你什么意思, 先生, 冒用我的命令?
What do you mean, sir,taking over my command?

586
00:49:06,360 --> 00:49:09,320
非常无礼, 你知道 -喔，上校, 我--我很抱歉...
Highly irregular, you know  - Oh, Colonel, I-I'm sorry...

587
00:49:09,440 --> 00:49:12,990
可是, 可是我需要你的帮助  -哦，没门
but, but I need your help  - Oh, absolutely impossible.

588
00:49:13,120 --> 00:49:16,660
我们在越野行军 - 但是这很紧急，上校
We're on a cross-county march  - But it's an emergency, Colonel.

589
00:49:16,790 --> 00:49:20,580
一定要找到那个人兽 - 人兽？什么人兽？
The man cub must be found - Man cub? What man cub?

590
00:49:20,960 --> 00:49:25,800
真有趣  - 我正要送回人类村庄的那个
How interesting  -The one I was taking to the man village.

591
00:49:26,170 --> 00:49:28,260
好, 那是他应该呆的地方.
Good. That's where he belongs.

592
00:49:28,430 --> 00:49:30,260
先生,如果你不介意...
Now, sir, If you don't mind...

593
00:49:30,430 --> 00:49:32,260
我们要继续行军了
we'd like to get on with the march.

594
00:49:32,390 --> 00:49:35,850
不，不，不，你 你不了解，哈索
No, no, no, you, you don't understand, Hathi.

595
00:49:35,980 --> 00:49:39,480
他走丢了，他跑了
He is lost. He ran away.

596
00:49:39,610 --> 00:49:41,730
真不错
How delightful.

597
00:49:41,900 --> 00:49:45,200
好吧，自以为是的年轻人经常如此
Well, serves the young whippersnapper right.

598
00:49:45,320 --> 00:49:48,200
但是，但是，歇尔可汗，那只可怕的老虎--
But, but Shere Khan, the tiger--

599
00:49:48,370 --> 00:49:50,830
他一定会找到这个人兽踪迹的
He's sure to pick up the man cub's trail.

600
00:49:52,960 --> 00:49:55,210
歇尔可汗？胡说, 伙计
Shere Khan. Nonsense, old boy.

601
00:49:55,340 --> 00:49:58,260
这几英里范围内不会出现歇尔可汗
Shere Khan isn't within miles of here.

602
00:50:01,380 --> 00:50:03,390
哦，抱歉，巴吉拉
Oh, sorry, Bagheera.

603
00:50:03,720 --> 00:50:05,680
战争的命运, 诸如此类的事,你知道
Fortunes of war, and all that sort of thing, you know.

604
00:50:05,810 --> 00:50:10,900
够了！够了！
This has gone far enough. Far enough.

605
00:50:11,020 --> 00:50:14,730
等等, 你这个饶舌的老家伙
Now just a minute, you pompous old windbag.

606
00:50:15,530 --> 00:50:19,030
威尼弗雷德！你不在队伍中，在干什么？
Winifred! What are you doing out of ranks?

607
00:50:19,200 --> 00:50:21,120
别管这个！
Never mind.

608
00:50:21,290 --> 00:50:23,290
你要把我们的孩子怎么样――
How would you like to have our boy...

609
00:50:23,410 --> 00:50:25,620
把他一个人丢在丛林中？
lost and alone in the jungle?

610
00:50:25,790 --> 00:50:29,040
我们的儿子？好吧--
Our son? W-Well--

611
00:50:29,160 --> 00:50:32,460
但是，威尼弗雷德老太婆，那完全不一样
But, Winifred old girl, that's an entirely different matter.

612
00:50:32,620 --> 00:50:35,380
哼！- 不一样，完全不一样
Huh! - Different, entirely.

613
00:50:35,500 --> 00:50:39,090
那个小男孩跟我们的儿子没有两样
That little boy is no different than our own son.

614
00:50:39,210 --> 00:50:42,880
现在你帮忙找到他，否则我接管指挥权
Now you help find him, or I'm taking over command.

615
00:50:43,050 --> 00:50:45,710
什么！一头母象来领导我的部队?
What! A female leading my herd?

616
00:50:45,720 --> 00:50:46,980
太可笑了
Utterly preposterous.

617
00:50:47,150 --> 00:50:50,150
爸爸？那个人兽和我是好朋友
Pop? The man cub and I are friends.

618
00:50:50,930 --> 00:50:53,590
如果我们不找到他，他会受到伤害的
He'll get hurt If we don't find him.

619
00:50:53,680 --> 00:50:56,300
求你了，爸爸？长官 求你了？
Please, Pop? Sir? Please?

620
00:50:56,430 --> 00:51:00,350
别担心，儿子。
Now don't you worry, son.

621
00:51:00,470 --> 00:51:04,060
你老爸早就有主意了
Your father had a plan in mind all the time.

622
00:51:06,520 --> 00:51:09,020
当然有。
Sure you did.

623
00:51:10,930 --> 00:51:14,890
士兵们！ 全队，向左转！
Troopers! Company, left face!

624
00:51:16,730 --> 00:51:18,980
志愿参加一项特殊任务的――
Volunteers for a special mission...

625
00:51:19,150 --> 00:51:21,020
向前一步走
will step one pace forward.

626
00:51:33,990 --> 00:51:37,320
那是我希望看到的，忠于职责
That's what I like to see. Devotion to duty.

627
00:51:38,820 --> 00:51:43,070
现在，你们志愿者要去找一个迷路的人兽
Now, you volunteers will find the lost man cub.

628
00:51:43,200 --> 00:51:46,330
哦，谢谢你，上校。 没时间可浪费了
Oh, thank you, Colonel. Now there's no time to lose.

629
00:51:46,450 --> 00:51:50,080
是的，是的 好吧，号手…
Yes, yes. Well, bugler.

630
00:51:50,240 --> 00:51:54,160
一看见人兽， 你就吹号…
When the man cub is sighted, you will sound your trumpet...

631
00:51:54,290 --> 00:51:56,450
三次  -是，长官
three times  - Yes, sir.

632
00:51:57,400 --> 00:51:59,110
不是现在，士兵
Not now, soldier.

633
00:51:59,250 --> 00:52:01,400
对不起，长官
Sorry, sir.

634
00:52:02,570 --> 00:52:07,530
中尉，我们的策略将出其不意
Lieutenant, our strategy shall be the element of surprise.

635
00:52:07,540 --> 00:52:10,290
你带一个班――
You will take one squad...

636
00:52:10,420 --> 00:52:13,840
搜寻右侧  -是，长官
and cover the right flank  - Yes, sir.

637
00:52:13,960 --> 00:52:16,300
我带另一个班――
And I shall lead the other squad...

638
00:52:16,460 --> 00:52:18,760
在左侧
on the left flank.

639
00:52:19,840 --> 00:52:23,510
很好。全队――
Very well. Company...

640
00:52:25,220 --> 00:52:27,760
向前走！
forward march!

641
00:52:37,350 --> 00:52:39,430
出其不意?
Element of surprise?

642
00:52:39,560 --> 00:52:41,640
哦，我说。
Oh, I say.

643
00:52:43,340 --> 00:52:48,170
那么现在，我要去和那个迷路的小人兽会合了
And now for my rendezvous with the little lost man cub.

644
00:54:15,770 --> 00:54:18,310
喀！是你！
Kaa! It's you!

645
00:54:18,440 --> 00:54:20,900
对，人兽
Yes, man cub.

646
00:54:21,020 --> 00:54:23,770
很高兴又见到你
So nice to see you again.

647
00:54:26,150 --> 00:54:28,980
哦，走开 让我一个人呆着
Oh, go away. Leave me alone.

648
00:54:29,940 --> 00:54:34,110
让我看看你
Let me look at you.

649
00:54:34,240 --> 00:54:37,990
不想让我看你?
You don't want me to look at you?

650
00:54:38,160 --> 00:54:40,990
那你看我吧
Then you look at me.

651
00:54:41,160 --> 00:54:44,160
不，先生，我知道你要干什么，咯――
No, sir. I know what you're tryin' to do, Kaa--

652
00:54:44,320 --> 00:54:47,080
你知道？恩，我是说――
You do? Uh, I mean...

653
00:54:47,200 --> 00:54:49,990
你不相信我 -不
you don't trust me  - No.

654
00:54:50,160 --> 00:54:54,000
那我可就没法帮你了
Then there's nothing I can do to help.

655
00:54:54,310 --> 00:54:56,150
你想帮我?
You wanna help me?

656
00:54:57,120 --> 00:54:58,330
当然了
Certainly.

657
00:54:58,500 --> 00:55:03,500
我看得出来你从来没有离开过这个丛林
I can see to it that you never have to leave this jungle.

658
00:55:04,460 --> 00:55:06,500
你怎么知道?
How could you do that?

659
00:55:06,670 --> 00:55:09,630
恩？哦，我有自己的――
Hmm? Oh, I have my own...

660
00:55:10,500 --> 00:55:13,630
小窍门
subtle little ways.

661
00:55:15,760 --> 00:55:19,630
但是首先 你得相信我
But first, you must trust me.

662
00:55:20,800 --> 00:55:22,760
我不再相信任何人了
I don't trust anyone any more.

663
00:55:24,130 --> 00:55:26,680
我不怪你
