这样的勇气应该得到一个公平的比赛机会
And such spirit is deserving of a sporting chance.

844
01:07:21,450 --> 01:07:25,150
现在，我闭上眼睛数到十
Now, I'm going to close my eyes and count to ten.

845
01:07:25,150 --> 01:07:27,800
这会使追捕变得更加有趣...
It makes the chase more interesting...

846
01:07:27,930 --> 01:07:29,800
对我来说
for me.

847
01:07:29,930 --> 01:07:33,560
一，二---
One, two...

848
01:07:33,680 --> 01:07:36,060
三---
three...

849
01:07:36,370 --> 01:07:39,040
四---
four--

850
01:07:39,680 --> 01:07:40,680
你在考验我的耐心
You're tying my patience.

851
01:07:41,040 --> 01:07:43,790
五，六，七，八，九，十！
Five, six, seven, eight, nine, ten!

852
01:07:47,510 --> 01:07:49,720
跑，毛戈力，快跑！
Run, Mowgli. Run!

853
01:07:49,790 --> 01:07:52,690
躲开, 你这个笨蛋
Let go, you big oaf.

854
01:07:52,860 --> 01:07:56,110
别紧张。拿着-- 呜！抓住，抓住
Take it easy. Take it-- Whoo! Ho-Hold it, hold it.

855
01:07:56,280 --> 01:08:00,530
哇。慢一点。呵！约！哇！慢！现在好了。
Whoa. Slow down. Ooh! Yow! Whoa! Slow! Easy now.

856
01:08:00,690 --> 01:08:02,650
呵，噢，孩子，好了
Ooh. Oh, boy. Easy.

857
01:08:02,780 --> 01:08:04,650
他抓住了老虎尾巴，他抓到了
He's got a tiger by the tail, he has.

858
01:08:04,820 --> 01:08:06,740
最好抓得够紧
And he'd better hang on too.

859
01:08:12,000 --> 01:08:14,250
看打, 你这个欺软怕硬的家伙
Take that, ya big bully.

860
01:08:14,260 --> 01:08:17,200
打他, 孩子,再打他, 孩子， 继续!
Let him have it again, kid. Hit him again, kid. Go on!

861
01:08:19,120 --> 01:08:21,700
布鲁！救我！
Baloo! Help me!

862
01:08:34,750 --> 01:08:37,000
谁来救救这孩子
Somebody do somethin' with that kid.

863
01:08:37,170 --> 01:08:39,130
来吧，伙计们
Come on, lads.

864
01:08:43,010 --> 01:08:45,380
他现在安全了
He's safe now.

865
01:08:45,510 --> 01:08:47,550
你可以放开了，布鲁
You can let go, Baloo.

866
01:08:47,670 --> 01:08:51,380
你在开玩笑? 老虎的牙可不是吃素的
Are you kiddin'? There's teeth in the other end.

867
01:08:57,680 --> 01:08:59,550
我要杀了你
I'll kill you for this.

868
01:09:01,560 --> 01:09:03,560
放开我！布鲁需要帮助！
Let go! Baloo needs help!

869
01:09:08,850 --> 01:09:11,520
火! 那是那老虎唯一害怕的
Fire! That's the only thing old Stripes is afraid of.

870
01:09:11,640 --> 01:09:13,890
你去取火，剩下的由我来.
You get the fire. We'll do the rest.

871
01:09:20,400 --> 01:09:23,570
冲啊！-去那边！拳打！脚踢！
Charge! - You there, punch and blow.

872
01:09:23,690 --> 01:09:26,320
滚开,你们这些笨蛋
Stay out of this, you mangy fools.

873
01:09:26,480 --> 01:09:30,110
是，是 它差一点
Yeah, yeah. Missed me a mile, he did.

874
01:09:30,280 --> 01:09:33,280
是！- 是！扯他那亮亮的胡须
Yeah!- Yeah! Pull his blinkin' whiskers.

875
01:09:34,180 --> 01:09:36,140
他是个讨厌的大猫，的确是！
He's a bloomin' pussycat, he is.

876
01:09:36,310 --> 01:09:39,100
看看你的身后,朋友
Look behind you, chum.

877
01:09:56,960 --> 01:09:59,050
他的末日到了
Well, that's the last of him.

878
01:10:00,920 --> 01:10:03,210
老斑毛离开就像一颗燃烧的彗星，的确是
Old Stripes took off like a flaming comet, he did.

879
01:10:03,640 --> 01:10:07,180
来吧. 让我们祝贺我们的朋友
Well, come on. Let's go congratulate our friend.

880
01:10:07,220 --> 01:10:09,100
等等, 伙计们
Hold it, fellas.

881
01:10:09,230 --> 01:10:13,060
现在还不是时候，看
Now's not the time for it. Look.

882
01:10:18,780 --> 01:10:21,490
布鲁？
Baloo?

883
01:10:28,920 --> 01:10:34,100
布鲁，起来啦 哦，请起来啦
Baloo, get up. Oh, please get up.

884
01:10:44,230 --> 01:10:47,270
毛戈力，试着理解
Mowgli, try to understand.

885
01:10:47,440 --> 01:10:50,020
巴吉拉，他怎么啦？
Bagheera, what's the matter with him?

886
01:10:50,150 --> 01:10:54,110
你要勇敢点，就像布鲁那样
You've got to be brave, like Baloo was.

887
01:10:54,230 --> 01:10:56,900
你--你不是说--
You-- You don't mean--

888
01:10:57,030 --> 01:11:00,530
别这样，别这样。布鲁
Oh, no. Baloo.

889
01:11:05,880 --> 01:11:08,050
现在，现在
Now, now.

890
01:11:08,860 --> 01:11:10,320
我理解你的感受
I know how you feel.

891
01:11:11,930 --> 01:11:14,060
但是你必须记住 毛戈力--
But you must remember, Mowgli...

892
01:11:14,910 --> 01:11:17,620
没有哪种更伟大的爱--
greater love hath no one...

893
01:11:17,740 --> 01:11:21,370
比得上为朋友牺牲生命
than he who lays down his life for his friend.

894
01:11:23,280 --> 01:11:27,070
当伟大的功绩被这个丛林记住...
When great deeds are remembered in this jungle...

895
01:11:27,240 --> 01:11:31,490
有一个名字高高在上
one name will stand above all others--

896
01:11:31,620 --> 01:11:35,830
我们的朋友, 布鲁, 一只伟大的熊.
our friend, Baloo, the bear.

897
01:11:37,170 --> 01:11:40,170
他真煽情 - 布鲁给我们的记忆...
He's crackin' me up  - The memory of Baloo's...

898
01:11:40,340 --> 01:11:42,170
它的勇敢和牺牲...
sacrifice and bravey...

899
01:11:42,340 --> 01:11:46,760
将永远铭刻在我们的心上.
will forever be engraved on our saddened hearts.

900
01:11:46,880 --> 01:11:51,590
太棒了 - 布鲁倒下的地方--
Beautiful - This spot where Baloo fell...

901
01:11:52,150 --> 01:11:56,270
将成为丛林里的圣地...
will always be a hallowed place in the jungle...

902
01:11:56,440 --> 01:11:59,240
因为这里躺着自然界--
for there lies one of nature's...

903
01:11:59,410 --> 01:12:01,240
最高尚的动物
noblest creatures.

904
01:12:04,160 --> 01:12:06,910
我希望我妈妈能听到这些
I wish my mother could've heard this.

905
01:12:07,150 --> 01:12:10,210
现在我们得走了
It's best we leave now.

906
01:12:10,340 --> 01:12:12,310
过来，人兽
Come along, man cub.

907
01:12:12,480 --> 01:12:15,310
嘿，别就不说了，巴吉拉 你说得太感人了！
Hey, don't stop now, Baghee. You're doin' great!

908
01:12:15,440 --> 01:12:18,220
再说一些，继续说吧
There's more, lots more.

909
01:12:19,260 --> 01:12:21,480
什么, 你这个大骗子!
Why, you big fraud!

910
01:12:22,020 --> 01:12:23,930
你 你 你这个装模做样的家伙!
You, you, you four-flusher!

911
01:12:24,060 --> 01:12:26,230
我-我受够了--我--
I-I'm fed up, and I-I--

912
01:12:26,400 --> 01:12:29,900
布鲁！你没事！
Baloo! You're all right!

913
01:12:30,070 --> 01:12:33,200
谁，我吗？我当然没事
Who, me? Sure I am.

914
01:12:33,320 --> 01:12:35,620
感觉不能再好了
Never felt better.

915
01:12:39,360 --> 01:12:41,320
你的确让我们担心
You sure had us worried.

916
01:12:41,450 --> 01:12:43,990
哦，我只是休息了一下
Ah, I was just takin' five.

917
01:12:44,160 --> 01:12:47,380
你知道吗, 刚才很过瘾.
You know, playin' it cool.

918
01:12:47,550 --> 01:12:49,430
是的，那老虎不堪一击
Yeah, but he was too easy.

919
01:12:49,460 --> 01:12:51,450
你真好，熊爸爸
Good old Papa Bear.

920
01:12:52,010 --> 01:12:54,890
没有这个小家伙，有些无趣，是不是?
It's going to be a bit dull without the little bloke, isn't it?

921
01:12:55,100 --> 01:12:57,160
耶。那么我们干什么呢？
Yeah. So what we gonna do?

922
01:12:57,330 --> 01:13:01,230
不知道 嘿，别又来了
I don't know. Hey, now, don't start that again!

923
01:13:01,960 --> 01:13:05,250
嘿，巴吉拉， 你错过这次行动真太惨了
Hey, Baghee, too bad you missed the action.

924
01:13:05,820 --> 01:13:09,530
你要是看见我把那该死的老虎打得落花流水就好了
You should have seen how I made a sucker out of old Stripes with that left up in his face.

925
01:13:09,660 --> 01:13:12,130
隆，隆 我就是这样揍他
Boom, boom, I was givin' him. Whang!

926
01:13:13,290 --> 01:13:15,420
你知道吗？我们是一对好伙伴
You wanna know somethin'? We're good sparrin' partners.

927
01:13:15,580 --> 01:13:17,250
你最好知道这一点
You'd better believe it.

928
01:13:17,630 --> 01:13:19,210
是，先生
Yes, sir.

929
01:13:19,300 --> 01:13:23,930
没有什么能够分开我们.
Nothin' or nobody is ever gonna come between us again.

930
01:13:25,100 --> 01:13:28,430
我的家园
My own home

931
01:13:28,560 --> 01:13:32,100
我的家园
My own home

932
01:13:32,810 --> 01:13:35,470
我的家园
My own home

933
01:13:36,070 --> 01:13:39,470
我的家园
My own home

934
01:13:41,030 --> 01:13:45,120
看，那是什么？ - 噢，是人类村庄
Look. What's that? - Oh, it's the man village.

935
01:13:45,250 --> 01:13:47,620
不，不，我指的那个
No, no. I mean that.

936
01:13:49,420 --> 01:13:53,920
忘记那些，他们只会给你带来麻烦.
Forget about those. They ain't nothin' but trouble.

937
01:13:54,090 --> 01:13:56,480
等一下 我以前从来没有见过
Just a minute. I've never seen one before.

938
01:13:57,140 --> 01:13:59,970
现在你看到了，我们走吧
So you've seen one. So let's go.

939
01:14:00,100 --> 01:14:03,480
我很快就回来，让我好好看看.
I'll be right back.I want a better look.

940
01:14:03,640 --> 01:14:06,150
毛戈力，等一下 - 噢，布鲁
Mowgli, wait a minute - Ah, Baloo.

941
01:14:06,320 --> 01:14:08,160
就让他好好看一下
Let him have a better look.

942
01:14:16,490 --> 01:14:20,080
爸爸在林中打猎
Father's hunting in the forest

943
01:14:20,200 --> 01:14:23,910
妈妈在家中做饭
Mother's cooking in the home

944
01:14:24,080 --> 01:14:27,660
我要去打水
I must go to fetch the water

945
01:14:27,790 --> 01:14:31,500
直到有一天我长大成人
Till the day that I am grown

946
01:14:31,620 --> 01:14:35,330
直到我长大成人
Till I'm grown

947
01:14:35,500 --> 01:14:39,000
直到我长大成人
Till I'm grown

948
01:14:39,130 --> 01:14:43,090
我要去打水
I must go to fetch the water

949
01:14:43,210 --> 01:14:47,630
直到我长大成人
Till the day that I am grown

950
01:15:04,970 --> 01:15:09,310
那时我会有个英俊的丈夫
Then I will have a handsome husband

951
01:15:09,430 --> 01:15:12,480
和一个我自己的女儿
And a daughter of my own

952
01:15:12,600 --> 01:15:16,480
我会让她来打水
And I'll send her to fetch the water

953
01:15:16,600 --> 01:15:20,900
我就在家中做饭
I'll be cooking in the home

954
01:15:27,780 --> 01:15:32,070
那时我派她去打水
Then I'll send her to fetch the water

955
01:15:32,190 --> 01:15:35,950
我就在家中做饭
I'll be cooking in my home

956
01:15:42,490 --> 01:15:45,240
她故意那样做的
She did that on purpose.

957
01:15:45,410 --> 01:15:47,240
很显然是
Obviously.

958
01:16:21,440 --> 01:16:25,490
毛戈力，回来，回来！
Mowgli, come back. Come back!

959
01:16:25,650 --> 01:16:27,300
继续走！继续走！
Go on! Go on!

960
01:16:52,350 --> 01:16:53,980
他被迷住了
He's hooked.

961
01:16:54,480 --> 01:16:57,400
哦，这是必然的，布鲁
Ah, it was inevitable, Baloo.

962
01:16:57,570 --> 01:17:01,410
这孩子已经无法自拔，这是命中注定的
The boy couldn't help himself. It was bound to happen.

963
01:17:01,530 --> 01:17:03,780
毛戈力到了他该去的地方了
Mowgli is where he belongs now.

964
01:17:04,990 --> 01:17:06,860
耶--
Yeah...

965
01:17:07,620 --> 01:17:10,040
我想你是对的
I guess you're right.

966
01:17:10,210 --> 01:17:14,010
但我仍然认为他可以做一只大熊
But I still think he'd have made one swell bear.

967
01:17:15,660 --> 01:17:17,870
好吧，巴吉老伙计
Well, come on, Baghee buddy.

968
01:17:18,040 --> 01:17:20,120
让我们回到属于我们的地方...
Let's get back to where we belong...

969
01:17:20,290 --> 01:17:22,790
跟着节拍...
and get with the beat.

970
01:17:22,950 --> 01:17:25,750
寻找必需品
Look for the bare necessities

971
01:17:25,870 --> 01:17:28,000
最基本的必需品
The simple bare necessities

972
01:17:28,170 --> 01:17:32,080
忘却你的忧虑和矛盾
Forget about your worries And your strife

973
01:17:32,210 --> 01:17:34,920
我的意思是最基本的必需品
I mean the bare necessities

974
01:17:35,000 --> 01:17:37,210
是自然的力量
Are Mother Nature's recipes

975
01:17:37,340 --> 01:17:40,710
将带来生活最起码的必需品
That bring the bare necessities of life


